        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "Salvation is the Jews' victory over human limitations: ignorance or insensitivity. It is the conquest\nof sinfulness, of the evils resident within the self: pride, selfishness, hate, lust, cynicism, the\ndeliberate rejection of goodness and truth. Milton Steinberg",
          "language": "en"
        }
